Package: covidtest
Title: COVID-19 Testing Strategy Assessment
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person('Jesse', 'Smith', email = 'Jesse.Smith@stjude.org', role = c('cre', 'aut')),
    person('Tomi',  'Mori',  email = 'Tomi.Mori@stjude.org',   role = 'aut'))
Description: Covidtest is a Shiny app that allows decision-makers to
    assess the benefits of performing asymptomatic testing in their
    organizations. It is primarily aimed at healthcare organizations,
    though it is applicable in a much wider range of settings.
